commits.name: cart
commits.content:
root = true

[*]
indent_style = space
indent_size = 2
end_of_line = lf
charset = utf-8
trim_trailing_whitespace = true
insert_final_newline = true
max_line_length = 200

[*.js]
block_comment_start = /*
block_comment = *
block_comment_end = */

[*.yml]
indent_size = 1

[package.json]
indent_style = tab

[CHANGELOG.md]
indent_style = space
indent_size = 2

[{*.json,Makefile}]
max_line_length = unset

[test/{dotdot,resolver,module_dir,multirepo,node_path,pathfilter,precedence}/**/*]
indent_style = unset
indent_size = unset
max_line_length = unset
insert_final_newline = unset
